Job Postings
The Fayette County Board of Education is accepting applications for the following positions posted today:

Berry Elementary Teacher;
Part time Fayette County High School Math Teacher;
Part time Fayette Middle School Science Teacher;
and 2 Bus Drivers.

Please see the board website at www.fayette.k12.al.us Select Our District, Job Openings, then Classified Jobs to view the actual job postings which includes qualifications and actual job responsibilities. The Teach In Alabama application link is listed there as well. APPLICATION must be made through the above online application site. For questions call (205) 932-4611, Ext. 232.
